[
  {
    "startTime": 3.903,
    "endTime": 4.6370000000000005,
    "text": "How do I look?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.7,
    "endTime": 7.941000000000001,
    "text": "Oh, um... I don't care."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.811,
    "endTime": 12.5,
    "text": "There's Lorraine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.0,
    "endTime": 14.681000000000001,
    "text": "Okay, now remember, no trading."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.148,
    "endTime": 17.0,
    "text": "You get the pretty one, I get the mess."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.416,
    "endTime": 19.652,
    "text": "- Hi, Joey.  - Hey."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.488,
    "endTime": 23.59,
    "text": "Well, well."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.157,
    "endTime": 25.759,
    "text": "Look what you brought."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.125,
    "endTime": 27.927,
    "text": "Very nice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.3,
    "endTime": 30.597,
    "text": "And what did you bring?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.0,
    "endTime": 33.5,
    "text": "She's checking her coat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.134,
    "endTime": 37.67,
    "text": "Joey, I'm gonna go wash the cab smell off my hands."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.7,
    "endTime": 41.207,
    "text": "Will you get me a White Zinfandel and a glass of red for Janice?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.212,
    "endTime": 47.147000000000006,
    "text": "Janice?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.379,
    "endTime": 48.882,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.215,
    "endTime": 50.85,
    "text": "Janice?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.018,
    "endTime": 56.689,
    "text": "Oh. My. God."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.326,
    "endTime": 62.796,
    "text": "Hey, it's Janice!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.536,
    "endTime": 71.504,
    "text": "You know..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.138,
    "endTime": 76.81,
    "text": "... ever since I was little, I've been able to pick up quarters with my toes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.9,
    "endTime": 78.0,
    "text": "Yeah?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.177,
    "endTime": 79.679,
    "text": "Good for you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.881,
    "endTime": 85.819,
    "text": "Uh, quarters or rolls of quarters?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.9,
    "endTime": 93.10000000000001,
    "text": "By the way, Chandler"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.2,
    "endTime": 99.399,
    "text": "I cut you out of all my pictures, so if you want, I have a bag with just your heads."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.8,
    "endTime": 101.601,
    "text": "That's okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.0,
    "endTime": 103.8,
    "text": "Oh, are you sure? Really?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.9,
    "endTime": 110.07600000000001,
    "text": "Because, you know, you could make little puppets out of them and you could use them in your theater of cruelty!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.2,
    "endTime": 114.38000000000001,
    "text": "We can't do that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.947,
    "endTime": 117.55,
    "text": "What? What can't you do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.452,
    "endTime": 122.455,
    "text": "Uh, can I talk to you for a second over there?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.927,
    "endTime": 129.929,
    "text": "Uh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.1,
    "endTime": 132.465,
    "text": "We might be leaving now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.0,
    "endTime": 135.101,
    "text": "Tell me it's you-and-me we."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.202,
    "endTime": 140.0,
    "text": "She said she wants to slather my body with stuff and then lick it off."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.1,
    "endTime": 142.775,
    "text": "I'm not even sure what \"slathering\" is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.6,
    "endTime": 146.112,
    "text": "But I definitely want to be a part of it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.7,
    "endTime": 150.416,
    "text": "Okay, you cannot do this to me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.784,
    "endTime": 153.2,
    "text": "You're right; I'm sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.2,
    "endTime": 158.458,
    "text": "Uh, can we have three chocolate mousses to go, please?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.325,
    "endTime": 160.493,
    "text": "I'm out of here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.6,
    "endTime": 161.7,
    "text": "Look..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.7,
    "endTime": 163.82899999999998,
    "text": "... here's my credit card."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.063,
    "endTime": 166.065,
    "text": "Dinner's on me; I'm sorry, Chandler."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.4,
    "endTime": 168.80100000000002,
    "text": "I hope she throws up on you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.1,
    "endTime": 172.5,
    "text": "Thanks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.64,
    "endTime": 175.909,
    "text": "So."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.9,
    "endTime": 177.34300000000002,
    "text": "Just us."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.7,
    "endTime": 179.646,
    "text": "Ugh, what a crappy night!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.2,
    "endTime": 186.7,
    "text": "Although, I have enjoyed the fact that, uh, your shirt's been sticking out of your zipper ever since you came back from the bathroom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.5,
    "endTime": 194.127,
    "text": "Excuse me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.3,
    "endTime": 198.99800000000002,
    "text": "How you doing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.7,
    "endTime": 204.43699999999998,
    "text": "So..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.338,
    "endTime": 207.2,
    "text": "... do we have the best friends or what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.6,
    "endTime": 209.29999999999998,
    "text": "Joey's not a friend; he's..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.8,
    "endTime": 215.3,
    "text": "... a stupid man who left us his credit card."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.8,
    "endTime": 220.286,
    "text": "Another drink? Some dessert? A big-screen TV?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.7,
    "endTime": 222.39999999999998,
    "text": "I will go for that drink."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.5,
    "endTime": 224.2,
    "text": "You got it. Good woman!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.6,
    "endTime": 232.0,
    "text": "Can we get a bottle of most overpriced champagne?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.3,
    "endTime": 234.0,
    "text": "- Each.  - That's right, each."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.1,
    "endTime": 236.5,
    "text": "Oh, and a, uh, Rob Roy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.6,
    "endTime": 239.072,
    "text": "I've always wanted to know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.1,
    "endTime": 261.02700000000004,
    "text": "Happy Valentine's Day!"
  }
]